title: INVERTA - Anthemic [2010] (320kbps)
description: INVERTA is a progressive hard-rock/metal band based out of Los Angeles, CA. The band was founded by guitarist Shawn Lickliter, bassist Chris Dunn and drummer Rorie D. van Klaveren.  In 2010, the band released two albums online which initiated the growth of their fan base, bringing forth a truly progressive sound with a metallic hard edge.  The balance heard in their work is sure to spark interest in both contemporary and post-rock/prog-metal fans alike.
